subtitleNullable: 92k anime faces sourced from safebooru then resized to 256x256
descriptionNullable:
Image data is sourced from safebooru.

Used some scuffed code and https://github.com/nagadomi/lbpcascade_animeface to extract faces from images, then resized to 256x256 and converted to jpg.

I think its fairly clean, if you want a very clean dataset I'd recommend sorting by size only only working with the largest files, as they tend to be faces more often than not.

It's just pure images without metadata
